title: Channel24.co.za | WATCH: Teens gobsmacked by Back to the Future reality!
text:
Cape Town – Kids of the 80s aren’t the only ones freaking out over Back to The Future Day! 
Today is 21 October 2015 the day Doc Brown (Christopher Lloyd) and McFly (Michael J. Fox) travelled to the future in Back to The Future II . 
In their latest video the Fine Brothers rounded up some millennials and showed them the trailer of the sequel. 
While most of them weren’t born yet when the movie was released they are familiar with the blockbuster trilogy of yesteryear. 
And their reaction when they realise that the movie's "future" actually takes place today is just priceless!
